  <h1 class="display display-xl" style="margin: 24px 0 0;">PM-32009 · iOS New Item Types stack</h1>
  <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 28px;">
    Six PRs across two branches, decided fast. Reviewer time is the bottleneck;
    this walkthrough leads with verdict and the <em>why</em>, with diffs underneath as
    drill-down detail. Plan to spend <strong>~18 minutes</strong> across the stack —
    most of that on the two sibling parsers (Driver's License, Passport).
  </p>

