        (#2573) → SDK bridge (#2576) → fork into Driver's License (#2577) and Passport (#2578).
        Tree B (#2582 → #2583) lifts <code>ExpandableHeaderView</code> from
        <code>AuthenticatorShared</code> into <code>BitwardenKit</code> so both apps can share
        one implementation. Tree B is independent of Tree A.
      </p>

